<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<FlexiPage xmlns="http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata">
    <flexiPageRegions>
        <itemInstances>
            <componentInstance>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>decorate</name>
                    <value>true</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Your organization works with &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;individuals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;households&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;organizations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; to carry out your mission. As an end user, you can track each of these stakeholders by creating Account records.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Individuals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; are represented as &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Person Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; records. We will use &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;individuals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; to mean &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Person Accounts&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. A &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Person Account &lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;is an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; record and also a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;contact&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; record, ensuring that anywhere in the system you need to reference an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;individual&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; (as either an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; record or as a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;contact&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; record), you can do so easily.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Additionally &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;groups&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; are represented as &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Business Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; records. Most organizations will have two types of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Business Accounts&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;organizations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;households&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. We will use &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;groups&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; to mean &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Business Accounts&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. The type of group is defined by a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Party Relationship Group&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; record that serves as an extension to the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; record.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentName>flexipage:richText</componentName>
                <identifier>flexipage_richText7</identifier>
            </componentInstance>
        </itemInstances>
        <name>Facet-madohxsd1n</name>
        <type>Facet</type>
    </flexiPageRegions>
    <flexiPageRegions>
        <itemInstances>
            <componentInstance>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>decorate</name>
                    <value>true</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;To install the Stakeholder Management Quick Start app you needed to create at least one &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Account record type&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; for &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Business Accounts&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; to enable &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Person&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Accounts&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Record types&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; provide users the choice to create an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;individual&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; or a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; and have different fields shown to them, and different picklist values. The &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;record&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;type&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; field is how the system identifies if an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; record represents an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;individual&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; or a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Go to Setup &amp;gt; Object Manager and select &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Person Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; (not &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;). Review &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;record types&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. Repeat for the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; object.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;It is best practice to have the minimum number of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;record types&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; possible across all objects, and for each &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;record type&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; to be distinct and exclusive. Meaning that an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;individual&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;group&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; cannot possibly fall under more than one &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;record type&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. We recommend two &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;record types&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, one under Account for &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Groups&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, and one under &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Person Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; for &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Individuals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. Only add additional &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;record types&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; if there is a clear business need. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentName>flexipage:richText</componentName>
                <identifier>flexipage_richText8</identifier>
            </componentInstance>
        </itemInstances>
