    <flexiPageRegions>
        <itemInstances>
            <componentInstance>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>decorate</name>
                    <value>true</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Individual relationships&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; are the most frequently used of the relationships. They allow you to connect &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;individuals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; to each other, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;households&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;organizations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Individual affiliations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; are how you connect &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;individuals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;households&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; and to &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;organizations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. These are most common to identify an &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;individual&apos;s&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;household&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, employer, or connection to other nonprofits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Group affiliations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; are relationships between two &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;groups&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;, either &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;households&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; or &lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;organizations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;. An extended family can be connected together using this type of relationship. Another example would be a corporate headquarters and their branches, or a national nonprofit organization and their local organizations. In these two examples the group affiliation compliments and adds additional detail to the &lt;/span&gt;&lt;em style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;Parent Account&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt; field.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
                </componentInstanceProperties>
                <componentName>flexipage:richText</componentName>
                <identifier>flexipage_richText5</identifier>
            </componentInstance>
        </itemInstances>
